ihkg.daarj.com&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=66a74744\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.daarj.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihk-forum.firebaseapp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flihk-forum.firebaseapp.com&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d78af6e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihk-forum.firebaseapp.com</a> （好奇怪，firefox同google-chrome都上唔到，但konqueror同epiphany上到）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.ddns.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.ddns.net&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b4e486af\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.ddns.net</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mysunshine.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/lihkg.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mysunshine.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Flihkg.html&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=5e7d8b21\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mysunshine.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/lihkg.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry, 你唔講, 我都唔知有最尾呢兩個web clients既存在! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 好似好陽春咁, 暫時取代唔到四大天王! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5e558038e3d2c3f21935a0ee1e6a73fffb590d","tid":54574,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://na.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8980a216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">na.cx</a> 有時回唔到post<br />\ndaarj 幾好幾快，係一開頭唔慣太逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660bc5efd0a304b27181b1cfb4b2874a50bb5dad","tid":54574,"uid":35271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:38:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"cff8a9213ef094fe92fe11972adbfba95b10a8a3","tid":54574,"uid":47426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:16:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e6a8df9c226debf8308d4269f99dfef776c5b52a","tid":54574,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T06:34:29.000Z","msg":"全部都係屎"},{"pid":"2026000acdfdbc2cb97c4f78f92bf775c0bff4bc","tid":54574,"uid":59747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"依家都用緊daarj, 雖然好對唔住個位巴打, 但係連巴整個個官方個介面真係最靚, 其次就係daarj, 依家都仲會用daarj 係因為回到post, 但我諗官方有得回覆我就會用番官方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735c2cc63d53496215b398428cc8baab29954b3a","tid":54574,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部都係屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屎係邊方面先?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講到出嚟, 大家又認同既, LIHKG既一眾developers一定會努力及時跟進 (唔似得亞JOE方丈咁嗌極都唔郁, 要等到差不多RIP先識嚟反應, 有L用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e7b742307bdd6a60b636ab55965785e9db59df","tid":54574,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話差，但感覺全部都app味好重，用電腦睇唔係幾順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2295e144ba2b28e2f3d4db429ab089546cd629","tid":54574,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話差，但感覺全部都app味好重，用電腦睇唔係幾順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家咩年代呀? app味重就當然架啦, 唔通要LIHKG既developers玩復古, 走番以前desktop-and-page-oriented web design既年代(we're living in an era of SPA and RWD, you know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )咩!? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab7e3b87733b5d0bc42d665a0169d8070d06b38","tid":54574,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係話差，但感覺全部都app味好重，用電腦睇唔係幾順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家咩年代呀? app味重就當然架啦, 唔通要LIHKG既developers玩復古, 走番以前desktop-and-page-oriented web design既年代(we're living in an era of SPA and RWD, you know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )咩!? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁不如直接出APP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nweb版就係俾你用電腦上家嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有,拋書包係咪會有道理D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204f689061e4532067216ec62f751c5e4355cad3","tid":54574,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://na.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8980a216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">na.cx</a> &gt; firebaseapp &gt;&gt; 官方 &gt; daarj <br />\n奇怪在無人做infinite scroll"},{"pid":"6767b187c93a478ee49e55d5c7696c2578a153a5","tid":54574,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係話差，但感覺全部都app味好重，用電腦睇唔係幾順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家咩年代呀? app味重就當然架啦, 唔通要LIHKG既developers玩復古, 走番以前desktop-and-page-oriented web design既年代(we're living in an era of SPA and RWD, you know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )咩!? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家冇人用 desktop PC?<br />\n日日對住個 moon 用 keyboard 寫 code 嗰班人用緊咩?<br />\n日日對住啲紙用 word processor 打文件嗰班人用緊咩?<br />\n你想講佢哋用緊 touch screen + mobile OS?<br />\n你唔係信 tim cock 嗰套呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7abc3183af26e20756fe0163bec2086b04f9d6d","tid":54574,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係話差，但感覺全部都app味好重，用電腦睇唔係幾順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家咩年代呀? app味重就當然架啦, 唔通要LIHKG既developers玩復古, 走番以前desktop-and-page-oriented web design既年代(we're living in an era of SPA and RWD, you know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )咩!? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家冇人用 desktop PC?<br />\n日日對住個 moon 用 keyboard 寫 code 嗰班人用緊咩?<br />\n日日對住啲紙用 word processor 打文件嗰班人用緊咩?<br />\n你想講佢哋用緊 touch screen + mobile OS?<br />\n你唔係信 tim cock 嗰套呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無啦啦彈句rwd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但rwd唔代表pc睇會係app樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁同電腦睇m版有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da867bd28062d2dccbbff749d72e1fc9be20b4f4","tid":54574,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"樓上果批desktop-manics係咪冬眠咗好耐？<br />\n用手機／平板上網既人數一早超越晒用desktop上網既，所以而家乜都mobile-first，SPA又好, RWD又好,  所有bleeding-edge front-end developments都係擁抱呢個原則, 以mobile device users行先, apps根本係主導緊成個市場, 大家醒未?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac13df6725f602706cded7d03a4800d4b1c090ed","tid":54574,"uid":21588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:29:05.000Z","msg":"App咪有LIHKG+ 咁屋企可唔可以有第2個介面呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af41888802b4b0a73cb62351c2f92650ae0f999b","tid":54574,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T20:55:32.000Z","msg":"daarj <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a47505378fed05515a7838a9f9f64ed64409cc","tid":54574,"uid":64571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上果批desktop-manics係咪冬眠咗好耐？<br />\n用手機／平板上網既人數一早超越晒用desktop上網既，所以而家乜都mobile-first，SPA又好, RWD又好,  所有bleeding-edge front-end developments都係擁抱呢個原則, 以mobile device users行先, apps根本係主導緊成個市場, 大家醒未?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁同高登某條傻鳩偏執desktop有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔明白點解有你呢類人<br />\n拋幾句野就以為自己睇撚通用家心態嘅傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我desktop做做下野休息<br />\nclick開個chrome開幾十個taps慢慢睇<br />\n會唔會爽過電話幾寸mon妹下妹下？<br />\n就算whatsapp而家都開埋web/desktop版大大巴刮落你度了<br />\n唔該唔好成日用有電視就無收音機既理論去諗野<br />\n明明mobile已經有app版<br />\n人地整web你覺得對象會係咩人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然係咁<br />\ndesktop用家講下意見有乜撚問題"},{"pid":"3218d54e27e8bfb3ebcb66c41d3881622ea74780","tid":54574,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"係唔係得我一個用平板上web板連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835b34a2438dc5988e9b9768d0b4bcfff4dac460","tid":54574,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"電腦睇官網好似以前ipad 開iphone apps咁<br />\n放大左咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔撚理你咩市場主導喇<br />\nDesktop 開嘅點都要似返desktop 用<br />\n利申 用開daarj<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日pm 叫佢fix bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執ui<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaec91bcdc1c740821e0627816758930ee986863","tid":54574,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電腦睇官網好似以前ipad 開iphone apps咁<br />\n放大左咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔撚理你咩市場主導喇<br />\nDesktop 開嘅點都要似返desktop 用<br />\n利申 用開daarj<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日pm 叫佢fix bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執ui<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常一個Front-end developer都知, 做desktop UI麻煩過晒時間過做mobile UI好多, 你估整LIHKG non-official web版果啲developers好L得閒, 定係你要人地特登自己科水買件似樣既desktop UI templates嚟服侍你班大帝!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c05ebd6e70129ccf277f24677f25bd10cf930f5","tid":54574,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔明點解唔整埋登入"},{"pid":"dc655a12eae9813e9201f2dfbcc35ff5034788a9","tid":54574,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電腦睇官網好似以前ipad 開iphone apps咁<br />\n放大左咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔撚理你咩市場主導喇<br />\nDesktop 開嘅點都要似返desktop 用<br />\n利申 用開daarj<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日pm 叫佢fix bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執ui<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常一個Front-end developer都知, 做desktop UI麻煩過晒時間過做mobile UI好多, 你估整LIHKG non-official web版果啲developers好L得閒, 定係你要人地特登自己科水買件似樣既desktop UI templates嚟服侍你班大帝!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常web唔會分mobile UI, desktop UI, 係睇 viewpoint size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係PC縮細個window就應該出所謂 ge mobile UI<br />\n難就難在係個responsive 果part，而唔係desktop UI templates<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7d3970935b12864aa7f472f71db86aeb2817b1","tid":54574,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://na.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8980a216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">na.cx</a> &gt; firebaseapp &gt;&gt; 官方 &gt; daarj <br />\n奇怪在無人做infinite scroll</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好撚奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95919a048061c03ec3abfc8668157ffa929b0c8","tid":54574,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://na.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8980a216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">na.cx</a> &gt; firebaseapp &gt;&gt; 官方 &gt; daarj <br />\n奇怪在無人做infinite scroll</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好撚奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b3220ea98985d9c62ab0f80c405845b24988d6","tid":54574,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電腦睇官網好似以前ipad 開iphone apps咁<br />\n放大左咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔撚理你咩市場主導喇<br />\nDesktop 開嘅點都要似返desktop 用<br />\n利申 用開daarj<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日pm 叫佢fix bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執ui<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常一個Front-end developer都知, 做desktop UI麻煩過晒時間過做mobile UI好多, 你估整LIHKG non-official web版果啲developers好L得閒, 定係你要人地特登自己科水買件似樣既desktop UI templates嚟服侍你班大帝!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常web唔會分mobile UI, desktop UI, 係睇 viewpoint size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係PC縮細個window就應該出所謂 ge mobile UI<br />\n難就難在係個responsive 果part，而唔係desktop UI templates<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要知道, 要responsive就難免唔follow mobile-first原則, 會令到個desktop UI(放大時)好apps樣/feel! 一係唔好玩responsive, desktop唔駛玩縮細, 就唔駛就mobile個頗為standardized既UI design; 但問題嚟喇, desktop都有好多款sizes, 又唔同scales(16:9, 16:10, 4:3, etc.), 唔通一款/scale做/買一個template??!! 你係non-official LIHKG web版developer, 冇錢收, 會唔會自找呢啲麻煩先?!! <br />\n<br />\n仲有, desktop UI design真係冇乜industrial standard可言(唔似mobile UI design咁, 一係android-like, 一係iOS-like, 有standard可follow!), 你叫developers點玩好? 一陣做到好似其他出名既forums樣咁, 連登仔又會走出嚟嘈, 指手劃腳, 畀說話人地聽! <br />\n<br />\n所以我話啲users唔好咁L多要求, 麻煩到一眾developer義士! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e750a13f676953b103c17ad21aa30606f70738","tid":54574,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常一個Front-end developer都知, 做desktop UI麻煩過晒時間過做mobile UI好多, 你估整LIHKG non-official web版果啲developers好L得閒, 定係你要人地特登自己科水買件似樣既desktop UI templates嚟服侍你班大帝!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常web唔會分mobile UI, desktop UI, 係睇 viewpoint size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係PC縮細個window就應該出所謂 ge mobile UI<br />\n難就難在係個responsive 果part，而唔係desktop UI templates<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要知道, 要responsive就難免唔follow mobile-first原則, 會令到個desktop UI(放大時)好apps樣/feel! 一係唔好玩responsive, desktop唔駛玩縮細, 就唔駛就mobile個頗為standardized既UI design; 但問題嚟喇, desktop都有好多款sizes, 又唔同scales(16:9, 16:10, 4:3, etc.), 唔通一款/scale做/買一個template??!! 你係non-official LIHKG web版developer, 冇錢收, 會唔會自找呢啲麻煩先?!! <br />\n<br />\n仲有, desktop UI design真係冇乜industrial standard可言(唔似mobile UI design咁, 一係android-like, 一係iOS-like, 有standard可follow!), 你叫developers點玩好? 一陣做到好似其他出名既forums樣咁, 連登仔又會走出嚟嘈, 指手劃腳, 畀說話人地聽! <br />\n<br />\n所以我話啲users唔好咁L多要求, 麻煩到一眾developer義士! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑撚左<br />\nUser 冇要求 就唔洗整喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDeveloper 就係想整好佢<br />\nUser 意見點都要有 <br />\n但佢受唔受就另一回事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知前問過daarj 果個點解唔整 auto paging <br />\n但佢話驚手機/ipad 用 chur resources 得濟<br />\n同埋做得developer 本身就係有段時間做呢d野先開個project 仔做下姐"},{"pid":"15ef7c2a87014be0cd815d11fff0e43299bd9274","tid":54574,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑撚左<br />\nUser 冇要求 就唔洗整喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDeveloper 就係想整好佢<br />\nUser 意見點都要有 <br />\n但佢受唔受就另一回事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知前問過daarj 果個點解唔整 auto paging <br />\n但佢話驚手機/ipad 用 chur resources 得濟<br />\n同埋做得developer 本身就係有段時間做呢d野先開個project 仔做下姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麻煩你先望望呢篇野：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bradfrost.com/blog/post/responsive-strategy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbradfrost.com%2Fblog%2Fpost%2Fresponsive-strategy%2F&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=365aabd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://bradfrost.com/blog/post/responsive-strategy/</a><br />\n<br />\n有乜好笑!? 本身LIHKG係mobile app,  咁理所當然web版用番Mobile-first Responsive Design既Strategy去盡量保留番app既原有features，實在係非常合理同自然既事。<br />\n<br />\n而家你似乎想反潮流，反自然，復古式咁叫人整番個類似以前廢老developers先會整既Desktop-only web版 LIHKG出嚟，咁駛唔駛整走埋啲mobile app features嚟洗走所有你地講既apps味呢？! <